flowRoot.flowPara: getting from point A to point B starts with a search of the end location, just like a regular search
As with every search, the bubble will appear above the location pin.
Pressing "Get directions to here" brings up the sidebar in step 3.
The sidebar pops up prefilled with "My current location" filled in with your location we figured out by Geolocation and To set to the location you searched for.
Mode of transportation could be automatically selected depending on distance (3 blocks vs. 200 km).
Clicking a stop in the list highlights the stop on the map.
